# ADR-002 — Separate Operation and Builder

## Status

Accepted

## Date

2026-07-01

## Context

The daily work environment (Windows) and the development environment (macOS) serve different purposes.

Mixing development tools into the work environment increases maintenance complexity and distracts from daily operations.

## Decision

Windows is designated as the Operation environment.

Responsibilities include:

- Enterprise WeChat
- Feishu
- Daily work
- Atlas usage

macOS is designated as the Builder environment.

Responsibilities include:

- GitHub
- Python
- MCP
- VS Code
- Atlas development
- Personal projects

## Consequences

### Positive

- Clear separation of responsibilities.
- Stable work environment.
- Flexible development environment.

### Negative

- Atlas synchronization will be postponed until the workflow is proven effective.
